      "comment": "DIVORCE PAPERS (2) flew the lids with a fast early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fourth (20.17) over 352m at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to her credit. Tough to beat if on-song. FARMOR ENVY (1) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 6th at this track in a Mix 5. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. WHISKEY CARTEL (3) unfancied latest but hit the ground running and gave a sight, holding on for a minor placing (19.28) at Q Straight in a Mix 5 over 350m. Leading chance. BIG ZEAL (4) jumps at a shorter trip and still warrants respect.",
